modName: Mini Quest The Great Mudcrab Hunt
summary: This mod adds a small quest and a new follower.
descriptionHtml: This mod adds a small quest and a new follower. The follower and the note that says where the giant mudcrab is, are in the Bannered Mare in Whiterun. Once you read the note you have to start searching for the Giant Mudcrab and kill it and claim the treasure
author: austin1298
